quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  111,1,"Perish the two hands of Abu Lahab, and perish he!"
  111,2,"Neither his wealth availed him, nor what he earned."
  111,3,"He will soon enter a fire, full of flames,"
  111,4,"and his wife as well, the wicked1 carrier of firewood."
  111,5,"In her neck there is a rope of twisted palm-fibre."
